Have you checked out our YouTube channel yet? NO? You should check it out! Especially while you wait online or inline for those Black Friday deals! and subscribe! #YouTube #sharethemusic #music #conversations #turnonthemusic #podcast

After the success of season one, our podcast; "An Eventful Life" is back! Checkout the first episode of the season 2 with Phil Ceberano. All the details are below.

🎧 Dive into these podcasts to stay ahead in the entertainment game! 🎤 🤖 Web3 and the Future of Music 🎭 Actors and the Digital Stage 😂 Comedy Goes Crypto 🎻 Virtual Concerts Unplugged Share your fave episode or tag a creator who should check these out! 🚀 #Web3 #LiveEntertainment #PromeetLive

Have you ever wondered why music is important to the profitability of your business? In Carlton Brunton’s latest podcast episode, we discuss: 🔶 Why music is important for your business. 🔶 The importance of 5 milliseconds. 🔶 How music makes you more memorable to your customers. 🔶 Why quality matters and how it reflects on your business. And a whole host of others things…like why AI is not coming for my job. https://lnkd.in/euqQk2Na
